ONCE UP ON THE TIME , IN A FOREST THERE LIVED A MONKEY WHO RESIDED ON A MANGO TREE WHICH WAS ON THE BANK'S OF A RIVER . IN THE SAME FOREST THERE LIVED A CROCODILE AND HIS WIFE . ONE DAY CROCODILE CAME TO THE BANKS OF THE RIVER AND RESTED UNDER THE TREE . THE KIND HEARTED MONKEY OFFERED HIM SOME FRUITS . THE CROCODILE CAME BACK THE NEXT DAY FOR MORE MORE FRUITS AS HE LOVED THEN.
